column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z, d.logMass,  s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift, GN.distance FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#,#, #) AS GN ON p.objID = GN.objID JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranEarlyNoDust AS d ON d.specObjID = s.bestobjid WHERE  s.z between # and # ORDER BY distance
